Package com.penthera.virtuososdk.client.database

Class PlaylistColumns

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.penthera.virtuososdk.client.database.PlaylistColumns
  • public class PlaylistColumns
extends Object
    The columns available to clients for querying the playlist cursor. Note that none of these columns can be updated via the content provider.
